org.eclipse.scada.configuration.infrastructure.impl

Class OptionsImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
      • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.infrastructure.impl.OptionsImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Options

    public class OptionsImpl
extends MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements Options
    An implementation of the model object 'Options'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Base Da Ngp Port
    • Base Ae Ngp Port
    • Base Ca Ngp Port
    • Base Hd Ngp Port
    • Monitor Pools
    • Event Pools
    • Default User Service
